"title":"The Forbidden Kingdom","video":false,"overview":"An American teenager who is obsessed with Hong Kong cinema and kung-fu classics makes an extraordinary discovery in a Chinatown pawnshop: the legendary stick weapon of the Chinese sage and warrior, the Monkey King. With the lost relic in hand, the teenager unexpectedly finds himself travelling back to ancient China to join a crew of warriors from martial arts lore on a dangerous quest to free the imprisoned Monkey King.","genre_ids":[28,12,14],"popularity":3.493,"vote_count":1865,"poster_path":"/z8chF1Z7hyuSVqLYTgElkQZh2VB.jpg","release_date":"2008-04-17","vote_average":6.623,"backdrop_path":"/9a59H9qoAzMcj1NWurMgvg9iLaT.jpg","original_title":"The Forbidden Kingdom","original_language":"en"},{"id":1885,"adult":false,"title":"The Karate Kid","video":false,"overview":"New Jersey teen Daniel LaRusso moves to Los Angeles with his mother, and soon strikes up a relationship with Ali. He quickly finds himself the target of bullying by a group of thugs, led by Ali's ex-boyfriend Johnny, who study karate at the Cobra Kai dojo under ruthless sensei John Kreese. Fortunately, Daniel befriends Mr. Miyagi, an unassuming repairman who just happens to be a martial arts master himself. Miyagi takes Daniel under his wing, training him in a more compassionate form of karate for self-defense and, later, preparing him to compete against the brutal Cobra Kai.","genre_ids":[28,12,18,10751],"popularity":6.2323,"vote_count":4600,"poster_path":"/1mp4ViklKvA0WXXsNvNx0RBuiit.jpg","release_date":"1984-06-22","vote_average":7.216,"backdrop_path":"/j1xaeJZOEOiVBD1rk3dg4YaAk23.jpg","original_title":"The Karate Kid","original_language":"en"},{"id":1887,"adult":false,"title":"Marie Antoinette","video":false,"overview":"A retelling of the story of France’s iconic but ill-fated queen, Marie Antoinette - from her betrothal and marriage to Louis XVI at fifteen to her reign as queen at nineteen and ultimately the fall of Versailles.","genre_ids":[18,36],"popularity":3.6401,"vote_count":2905,"poster_path":"/cybXGmv8Rjd5Os8Xml6YxMBQ0Zt.jpg","release_date":"2006-05-24","vote_average":6.7,"backdrop_path":"/9hxBNoRjEDZGjyR1JpmmtxJWmVU.jpg","original_title":"Marie Antoinette","original_language":"en"},{"id":1904,"adult":false,"title":"Memoirs of a Geisha","video":false,"overview":"In the years before World War II, a penniless Japanese child is torn from her family to work as a maid in a geisha house.","genre_ids":[18,10749,36],"popularity":3.1767,"vote_count":3323,"poster_path":"/pBwYsQaSTgnPphIy02DJjCF2cqs.jpg","release_date":"2005-12-06","vote_average":7.644,"backdrop_path":"/zJDnqXtGNHUmexiaWNa52Vslve5.jpg","original_title":"Memoirs of a Geisha","original_language":"en"},{"id":2004,"adult":false,"title":"Kebab Connection","video":false,"overview":"In Hamburg, Ibrahim \"Ibo\" Secmez, of Turkish descent, wants to direct the first German kung-fu movie. For now, he makes commercials for his uncle's kebab restaurant. Titzie, an aspiring actress and Ibo's German girlfriend, finds she's pregnant. Ibo is uncertain about fatherhood - compounded by his father's disowning him for getting a German girl pregnant - so Titzie sends him packing. He makes attempts at getting it right, but as the birth approaches, he's still not ready. In the background are three thugs in search of good tripe soup and a Capulet-Montegue feud between the kebab joint and a Greek taverna across the street. Can Ibo be the glove upon that hand?","genre_ids":[35,28,10749],"popularity":0.3822,"vote_count":71,"poster_path":"/jNHsAVtJEzAGQJnv3AGagBSAFLu.jpg","release_date":"2004-04-21","vote_average":6.655,"backdrop_path":"/s2XyJwZ2nmtbCT8ZE3oPlm0yq1j.jpg","original_title":"Kebab Connection","original_language":"de"},{"id":1061536,"adult":false,"title":"Detective Chen","video":false,"overview":"A rookie Shanghai police captain disguises himself as a student to investigate a murder at a local high school. However, he hates studying, Therefore he must juggle homework and solving the crime case.","genre_ids":[28,80,35,9648],"popularity":0.425,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/rRFzMI88IqxojpTFieneCPiqglg.jpg","release_date":"2022-12-15","vote_average":3.3,"backdrop_path":"/tmOoETLwjrUnb1EhvZ4LktD4Y3j.jpg","original_title":"逃学神探","original_language":"zh"},{"id":1966,"adult":false,"title":"Alexander","video":false,"overview":"Alexander, the King of Macedonia, leads his legions against the giant Persian Empire. After defeating the Persians, he leads his army across the then known world, venturing farther than any westerner had ever gone, all the way to India.","genre_ids":[10752,36,28,12,18,10749],"popularity":4.6286,"vote_count":3451,"poster_path":"/jrwQu72sGwGqwE8Ijne89PSIvhp.jpg","release_date":"2004-11-21","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/h21dxRjtR7xOhyZljtSYeTETCht.jpg","original_title":"Alexander","original_language":"en"},{"id":1941,"adult":false,"title":"Exodus","video":false,"overview":"Ari Ben Canaan, a passionate member of the Jewish paramilitary group Haganah, attempts to transport 600 Jewish refugees on a dangerous voyage from Cyprus to Palestine on a ship named the Exodus. He faces obstruction from British forces, who will not grant the ship passage to its destination.","genre_ids":[18,10752],"popularity":1.5323,"vote_count":220,"poster_path":"/1JXFJRztd43gCf4TAodNUwkfZoi.jpg","release_date":"1960-12-15","vote_average":6.67,"backdrop_path":"/9Knw79HXoPpHIqa9TscDlwbuRJV.jpg","original_title":"Exodus","original_language":"en"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt32649961","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":null,"instagram_id":null,"rotten_tomatoes_id":"m/blades_of_the_guardians"},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":148411,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"AU","release_dates